    "As a result, determining the WCET of the 6-DOF application directly is nearly impossible.",
    "Accordingly, used the above program to test if our RL algorithms can reach the input resulting in WCET of our sample program.",
    "RQ3 ConclusionThe GA outperformed the random algorithm in both the 6-DOF case study for estimating WCET and the CD case study..",
    "Furthermore, statistical analyses revealed that the reinforcement learning algorithms RL PPO ED and RL A2C ED significantly outperformed GA in the CD case study, with all p-values close to 0.",
    "This demonstrates that RL PPO ED and RL A2C ED are more effective than GA across various contexts."
